<subSubSection id="867FC4F8D15FAAE6A24875F99F598777" pageId="12" pageNumber="49" type="distribution">
<paragraph id="809C3173CB636A9E26728F168E6E893B" pageId="12" pageNumber="49">Distribution.</paragraph>
<paragraph id="E052D70202F49355DB08DC2EAA8AD3B5" pageId="12" pageNumber="49">Marquesas Islands, endemic to southern and central Fatu Hiva, 10-625 m.</paragraph>
